      <textAnnotation id="sid-F302E052-90AA-4738-9520-C817BEC50AA7" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>GTS check are applied on OBD</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-13CD9D4F-78C7-445C-A763-F9551273197A" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Buyer has the ability to replace a new buy MMID with a previously cleaned MMID within the VAS order</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-51AD1710-8703-4F8E-9AF0-92FF2F6799F5" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>If kit requires pre-cleaning, Buyer will add text instructions to place the completed kit blocked stock upon VAS completion</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-E534832D-27D0-43D6-86A2-4DF0C9EC573B" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Buyer Initiates the VAS order</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-3E18AABF-98FE-4F13-B861-5ACB761F2D8D" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>If Buyer has added text comments in the VAS order to place the kit in blocked stock, then warehouse will manually select blocked stock while performing put-away</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <group categoryValueRef="sid-d9cf3744-e822-4b91-9157-f4d51defcfb9" id="sid-DDA9CB34-20D2-4669-915B-AB949F87DBCF">
